Dotfiles
========

Curated configuration files and installer for i3/polybar/kitty/zsh/neovim.

Install (recommended)::

    git clone https://github.com/0xjah/Dotfiles.git ~/Dotfiles
    cd ~/Dotfiles
    chmod +x install.sh
    ./install.sh --dry-run
    ./install.sh --backup --symlink

Top-level contents::

    i3/    polybar/    kitty/    nvim/    rofi/    wallpapers/    install.sh

Report issues or feature requests via GitHub issues or pull requests.

